== Entering &quot;Factory data reset mode&quot; ==
# Turn off the device
# Press and hold Volume Down key + Power Key
# Release Power key when LG logo appear
# When still pressing Volume Down key, press and hold Power key again
# Release Volume Down key when Factory Data Reset menu appears

== Entering &quot;LG Download mode&quot; ==
# Turn off the device
# Press and hold Volume Up key
# Connect the USB cable
# Release Volume Up key when Download mode appears

